claim: Following completion of searches, the number of studies identified and volume of data to extract, meant that we deviated from the protocol and only used randomised designs for data extraction and synthesis (see Figure 1).

caption: PRISMA flow diagram. aIn contrast to the published protocol, pragmatic constraints meant that non‐randomised designs were ultimately excluded from the current review.
